{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Well, during this time, I already corresponded with, with all the people whose name I gave and whose names I found out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I, I corresponded with my uncle in Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was dying to go up to Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and he, he was writing, really, most welcoming letters to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- and-- but these people said, well, why don't you stay for-- at least, you should-- you need convalescing now.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you should be staying up here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I agreed to stay for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I, I stayed up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I went up to Paris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in Paris, I found that my uncle was a very poor man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, my uncle was my uncle because he married a sister of my mother, who was run over by a, a, a, a coach, by a bus, in 1935.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that by that time, really, he wasn't my uncle anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was-- he was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was married-- he had another wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the flat was absolutely full with her pictures, with my aunt's pictures.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And during the war, he was hiding and helping some of the family, some of my cousins who came through Paris.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was absolutely wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He behaved wonderfully.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And now, he had-- he was 62.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he had a wife who was 35.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, and they were wonderful to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were extremely poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were also very bohemian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, I can't go in to tell about my uncle, which is a lovely story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was-- they were so nice to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they really didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were so nice to me that I felt I had to do something.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
